Apple CEO Tim Cook today said Apple will be donating an undisclosed amount towards <a href="https://apnews.com/article/myanmar-bangkok-earthquake-0a2bd512bca189d034905566605989e9">earthquake</a> relief efforts in Myanmar and Thailand.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/03/Apple-Logo-Red.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-997127" /><br/>
"Our hearts go out to all those in Myanmar and Thailand affected by the devastating earthquake," said Cook, in a <a href="https://x.com/tim_cook/status/1906409440128930185">social media post</a>.<br/>
<br/>
